      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.archetypes.Item.sTWRGNQuZREcAe4H]{Doshko Specialist}</p>\n<p>The third tooth strives to prove the doshko a superior weapon. You gain a +2 bonus to attack rolls when performing @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.U37n5tY5hn1ctzQL.JournalEntryPage.R33uiOMesYP0ISWl#disarm]{disarm}, @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.U37n5tY5hn1ctzQL.JournalEntryPage.R33uiOMesYP0ISWl#sunder]{sunder}, or @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.U37n5tY5hn1ctzQL.JournalEntryPage.R33uiOMesYP0ISWl#trip]{trip} combat maneuvers with a doshko. If your attack roll is a natural 20, you also apply the doshko’s critical hit effect (if any) to the target.</p>"
